N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 163.11 - Compliance with other legal requirements

State Regulations

Compliance with the provisions of the rules and regulations
in this section shall not excuse failure to comply with the provisions of the

Federal Food, Drug and Cosmetic Act or with other laws and regulations
applicable within a marketing region. Notes
